Class is in session! Today we are stoked to link up with @maurcoy to learn the secrets of the Ollie from the Prince of Pop himself. From foot placement, to rolling vs stationary, Maurio breaks down everything about how he learned ollies, what runs through his head while he is getting ready to pop an ollie, and how the ollie applies to many other tricks in skateboarding. If you are just getting in to skating, this is a great first trick to learn. Let us know in the comments which tricks we should cover next, and swipe 🆙 in our story to join Maurio for our @youtube premiere!
🎥: @_nickhanson
🎬: @tylerlodzinski
#SantaCruzSkateboards
